des: Top Ten Chicago Restaurants is the 'top ten' Chicagoland restaurants from Restaurant Authority. Restaurant Authority is a meticulously curated directory of iconic and trending bars and restaurants in the Chicagoland area. Restaurant Authority also advocates for unique special events, industry happenings, and limited time only deals at selected Restaurants, Bars, and Venues.
